<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on {!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}&nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">Dear {!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c},&nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">Congratulations on being appointed as {!Job_placement__c.Role__c} on NCS with The Challenge on {!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}. +</span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Your total pay for this part of the role will be {!Job_placement__c.Total_gross_pay__c}, this includes pay for &nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Annual_Leave_entitlement__c} day(s), "Holiday Period"; per "Wave Contract", which is subject to tax and national insurance deductions.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">This payment will cover the following parts of the programme - &nbsp;NCS: Personal Challenge, NCS: Team Challenge and NCS: Real Challenge Design (one or more will be relevant to your role). Payments for NCS: The Real Challenge Action will be communicated to you at a later date once you have completed them. &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">You will be paid on {!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c}. Tax and NI deductions will be made from this payment. We reserve the right to deduct pay for any&nbsp;</span></font><span style="font-size: 12px;">unauthorised</span><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">&nbsp;absences.&nbsp;</span></font></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">You will receive further information about your pay relating to the NCS Real Challenge Action weekends and Graduation (if applicable) in due course.&nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">This payment structure has two principles:&nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">(a) to ensure that staff members pay the appropriate level of tax in the correct month and (b) to enable staff members to receive payment in reasonable time.&nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;">Yours sincerely,&nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">NCS with The Challenge&nbsp;</span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}&nbsp;</span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 11.818181991577148px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">2.4.1a</span></div></div></div>]]></td>
